<h2 class="bold font-l">Inquisition Song</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Torquemada enjoys torturing Jews (and Muslims) so much he wrote a song about it. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/VillainSong" class='trope-example-link'>Villain Song</a></p>
</div>
</div>
